'''光裂合酶'''（Photolyases，[[EC編號|EC]] 4.1.99.3）為一種[[DNA修復|DNA修復]][[酵素|酵素]]，專門修復遭受[[紫外線|紫外線]]破壞的DNA。此酵素的作用需要[[可見光|可見光]]協助活化<ref name="Yamamoto2017">{{cite journal|vauthors=Yamamoto J, Shimizu K, Kanda T, Hosokawa Y, Iwai S, Plaza P, Müller P|title=Loss of Fourth Electron-Transferring Tryptophan in Animal (6-4) Photolyase Impairs DNA Repair Activity in Bacterial Cells|journal=Biochemistry|volume=56|issue=40|pages=5356–5364|date=October 2017|pmid=28880077|pmc=|doi=10.1021/acs.biochem.7b00366}}</ref>及DNA修復<ref name="Thiagarajan2011">{{cite journal|vauthors=Thiagarajan V, Byrdin M, Eker AP, Müller P, Brettel K|title=Kinetics of cyclobutane thymine dimer splitting by DNA photolyase directly monitored in the UV|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|volume=108|issue=23|pages=9402–7|date=June 2011|pmid=21606324|pmc=3111307|doi=10.1073/pnas.1101026108 }}</ref>。光裂合酶修復DNA的過程稱為光學活作用（photoreactivation）。

由[[系統發生學|系統發生學]]來看，光裂合酶是一個相當古老的酵素，從[[細菌|細菌]]、[[真菌|真菌]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Teranishi, M.|first1=Nakamura, K., Morioka, H.,Yamamoto, K. and Hidema, J.|title=The native cyclobutane pyrimidine dimer photolyase of rice is phosphorylated|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-physiology_2008-04_146_4/page/1941|journal=Plant Physiology|date=2008|volume=146|issue=4|pages=1941–1951|doi=10.1104/pp.107.110189|pmid=18235036|pmc=2287361
}}</ref>，到[[動物|動物]]體內都有<ref name="Selby 17696–700">{{cite journal | vauthors = Selby CP, Sancar A | title = A cryptochrome/photolyase class of enzymes with single-stranded DNA-specific photolyase activity | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 103 | issue = 47 | pages = 17696–700 | date = November 2006 | pmid = 17062752 | pmc = 1621107 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0607993103 }}</ref>，且在植物體內尤為重要。人類等胎盤哺乳類體內則並無此酵素活性，而是使用另一種較無效率的[[核苷酸切除修復|核苷酸切除修復]]法來取代光裂合酶<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Lucas-Lledó JI, Lynch M | title = Evolution of mutation rates: phylogenomic analysis of the photolyase/cryptochrome family | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-biology-and-evolution_2009-05_26_5/page/1143 | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | volume = 26 | issue = 5 | pages = 1143–53 | date = May 2009 | pmid = 19228922 | pmc = 2668831 | doi = 10.1093/molbev/msp029 }}</ref>。

DNA中相鄰的[[胸腺嘧啶|胸腺嘧啶]]受到[[紫外線|紫外線]]的照射時，會形成[[共價鍵|共價鍵]]，形成[[環丁烷|環丁烷]]橋，稱為[[胸腺嘧啶二聚體|胸腺嘧啶二聚體]]。形成胸腺嘧啶二聚體的基因會導致基因在複製和轉錄時出現錯誤<ref>{{cite book | title = Biochemistry | first1 = Reginald H. | last1 = Garrett | first2 = Charles M. | last2 = Grisham | name-list-format = vanc |date=2010|publisher=Brooks/Cole, Cengage Learning|isbn=978-0-495-10935-8|oclc=984382855}}</ref>。光裂合酶會接在[[脱氧核糖核酸|DNA]]上，切除[[胸腺嘧啶二聚體|胸腺嘧啶二聚體]]，並修復回原本的樣子。

